          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-chris-pond" title="Mr Chris Pond">Mr. Pond</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I refer the hon. Member to the written answer I gave him on <a href="/written_answers/2003/dec/18/child-support-agency#column_1092w">18 December 2003,<span class="italic">Official Report,</span> column 1092W</a>.</p>
        </blockquote>
